Package: libatomspace-machspace
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libatomspace (>= 5.0.3),
         libcogutil (>= 2.0.3)
Description: MachSpace storage backend for OpenCog AtomSpace
 This package provides a distributed hypergraph storage backend
 that integrates OpenCog's AtomSpace with the HurdCog microkernel.
 .
 MachSpace enables kernel-level cognitive graph storage and
 provides IPC-based communication for AGI-OS integration.

Package: libatomspace-machspace-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         libatomspace-machspace (= ${binary:Version}),
         libatomspace-dev (>= 5.0.3),
         libcogutil-dev (>= 2.0.3)
Description: MachSpace storage backend development files
 Development files for the MachSpace storage backend.
 .
 This package contains headers and CMake configuration files
 needed to develop applications using MachSpace.
